00:01:42.240 --> 00:01:47.000 line:20%
ADAPTED FROM THE NOVEL <i>ZHU YU</i>
BY TUAN ZI LAI XI ON JJWXC.NET

00:01:51.680 --> 00:01:55.520 line:80%
Your Majesty, Chancellor Wei
and Grand Tutor Li request an audience.

00:02:00.160 --> 00:02:03.080 line:80%
What brings both of you to see me?

00:02:04.480 --> 00:02:08.120 line:80%
Your Majesty, I must impeach
Chancellor Wei's son, Wei Xuan.

00:02:08.200 --> 00:02:11.160 line:80%
He forcibly requisitioned winter grain,
sparked a revolt, and deserted the front.

00:02:11.240 --> 00:02:13.880 line:80%
He even returned to the capital without
authorization and killed innocent people.

00:02:13.960 --> 00:02:16.280 line:80%
Justice demands punishment.

00:02:19.160 --> 00:02:20.560 line:80%
Easy there, Grand Tutor.

00:02:21.640 --> 00:02:23.360 line:80%
What's this about killing innocent people?

00:02:23.440 --> 00:02:24.560 line:80%
Chancellor Wei!

00:02:25.440 --> 00:02:28.160 line:80%
Your son broke
my youngest grandson's legs.

00:02:28.240 --> 00:02:29.920 line:80%
He'll likely never walk right again.

00:02:30.000 --> 00:02:32.120 line:80%
Was that just following orders,

00:02:32.200 --> 00:02:33.880 line:80%
or was it a crime without punishment?

00:02:34.680 --> 00:02:35.520 line:80%
Your Majesty,

00:02:35.600 --> 00:02:39.200 line:80%
if someone in this court can cover the sky
with one hand and silence us,

00:02:39.280 --> 00:02:42.240 line:80%
then I will have no choice
but to beat the drum of justice

00:02:42.320 --> 00:02:45.280 line:80%
and let the whole realm
judge right from wrong.

00:02:45.360 --> 00:02:47.120 line:80%
-This…
-Good.

00:02:47.640 --> 00:02:50.240 line:80%
I will gladly accompany you.

00:02:50.960 --> 00:02:51.840 line:80%
Don't…

00:02:51.920 --> 00:02:54.760 line:80%
Your Majesty, I have endured
all kinds of humiliation

00:02:54.840 --> 00:02:56.400 line:80%
for the sake of your dignity.

00:02:56.480 --> 00:03:00.360 line:80%
But Li Huaiqin dared to say
that my wife and I are at odds,

00:03:00.440 --> 00:03:01.680 line:80%
that my son isn't really mine.

00:03:02.360 --> 00:03:05.160 line:80%
He even suggested that I harbor feelings
for a childhood sweetheart,

00:03:05.240 --> 00:03:06.160 line:80%
now in the inner palace,

00:03:06.240 --> 00:03:07.840 line:80%
dragging in matters

00:03:07.920 --> 00:03:10.880 line:80%
involving the previous emperor
and secrets of the harem.

00:03:11.720 --> 00:03:14.840 line:80%
And now the Li family
dares to speculate and slander?

00:03:15.360 --> 00:03:16.320 line:80%
Fine.

00:03:16.400 --> 00:03:19.400 line:80%
I'll go with you to the drum of justice.

00:03:19.480 --> 00:03:22.960 line:80%
Let's lay everything out clearly
before the whole realm.

00:03:23.040 --> 00:03:24.000 line:80%
Let's go.

00:03:24.640 --> 00:03:26.160 line:80%
You're lying!

00:03:26.240 --> 00:03:29.320 line:80%
When did the Li family ever
speculate about you and the harem…

00:03:30.360 --> 00:03:32.560 line:80%
Your Majesty, I did not. I did not!

00:03:32.640 --> 00:03:33.960 line:80%
You just said it,
and now you're saying you didn't?

00:03:34.040 --> 00:03:35.640 line:80%
Both of you, please calm down.

00:03:35.720 --> 00:03:36.880 line:80%
Let's discuss this properly.

00:03:36.960 --> 00:03:38.760 line:80%
Grand Tutor Li
fills the court with slander.

00:03:38.840 --> 00:03:40.520 line:80%
I fear even Your Majesty
can't see through it all.

00:03:40.600 --> 00:03:42.280 line:80%
You must answer for this.

00:03:42.360 --> 00:03:43.280 line:80%
Let's go.

00:03:43.360 --> 00:03:44.440 line:80%
-Your Majesty!
-Both of you…

00:03:44.520 --> 00:03:45.880 line:80%
-I am wronged!
-Who wronged you?

00:03:45.960 --> 00:03:47.280 line:80%
It's Wei Yan who deceives
those above and bullies those below.

00:03:47.360 --> 00:03:50.520 line:80%
He doesn't take Your Majesty
seriously at all! Your Majesty!

00:03:50.600 --> 00:03:52.040 line:80%
-Your Majesty!
-Please don't damage your rapport.

00:03:52.120 --> 00:03:53.000 line:80%
Your Majesty!

00:03:58.880 --> 00:04:02.160 line:80%
Fine. If no one will listen,
then I won't be emperor anymore.

00:04:04.320 --> 00:04:05.600 line:80%
-What if I abdicate? Would that work?
-Stop!

00:04:05.680 --> 00:04:06.520 line:80%
You can't.

00:04:09.080 --> 00:04:11.160 line:80%
As the Son of Heaven,

00:04:11.240 --> 00:04:12.480 line:80%
you can't just take off
the dragon robe like that.

00:04:12.560 --> 00:04:13.400 line:80%
What would people think?

00:04:14.600 --> 00:04:15.960 line:80%
How dare you, Wei Yan?

00:04:16.040 --> 00:04:19.440 line:80%
You dare speak to His Majesty like that?

00:04:20.040 --> 00:04:23.560 line:80%
I'd say you're the one who's out of line!

00:04:27.200 --> 00:04:28.160 line:80%
I am guilty.

00:04:28.840 --> 00:04:29.760 line:80%
Enough.

00:04:30.680 --> 00:04:32.880 line:80%
Both of you were caught up in the moment,

00:04:32.960 --> 00:04:34.840 line:80%
and so was I.

00:04:35.360 --> 00:04:38.440 line:80%
In the end, it's all because Li Huaiqin
couldn't hold his tongue when drunk.

00:04:41.880 --> 00:04:44.440 line:80%
But since his legs are already broken
and he's been punished,

00:04:44.520 --> 00:04:46.720 line:80%
I'll send an imperial physician
to treat him.

00:04:46.800 --> 00:04:48.160 line:80%
Once he recovers,

00:04:48.240 --> 00:04:49.880 line:80%
transfer him to the Imperial Academy
to reform through study

00:04:49.960 --> 00:04:50.800 line:80%
and cultivate virtue.

00:04:54.720 --> 00:04:57.520 line:80%
As for Wei Xuan injuring someone,

00:04:57.600 --> 00:04:59.600 line:80%
though the circumstances
may be understandable,

00:04:59.680 --> 00:05:01.880 line:80%
the law is the law.

00:05:01.960 --> 00:05:03.800 line:80%
Taking justice into your own hands
is wrong.

00:05:03.880 --> 00:05:07.200 line:80%
For now, let's remove him
from his post as Military Commissioner.

00:05:07.280 --> 00:05:09.040 line:80%
He can redeem himself
through future merit.

00:05:09.120 --> 00:05:10.160 line:80%
In any case,

00:05:11.480 --> 00:05:15.560 line:80%
if I hear any more foul talk involving
the royal family's honor again,

00:05:16.960 --> 00:05:18.040 line:80%
don't blame me for being ruthless.

00:05:23.560 --> 00:05:25.360 line:80%
I obey the decree.

00:05:39.320 --> 00:05:41.800 line:80%
-Your Majesty, they're gone.
-Bah!

00:05:43.400 --> 00:05:44.440 line:80%
Your Majesty, please calm down.

00:05:45.240 --> 00:05:46.280 line:80%
Your Majesty,

00:05:46.360 --> 00:05:50.120 line:80%
if things go on like this,
Grand Tutor Li might turn against you.

00:05:50.200 --> 00:05:51.320 line:80%
Then what would you have me do?

00:05:51.400 --> 00:05:52.440 line:80%
Tell me. What should I do?

00:05:52.520 --> 00:05:53.760 line:80%
What should you do?

00:05:55.160 --> 00:05:57.880 line:80%
With Xie Zheng back,
Wei Yan's got his spine again.

00:05:58.480 --> 00:06:00.760 line:80%
Coming here today, he was
clearly slapping me in the face,

00:06:00.840 --> 00:06:02.520 line:80%
trying to break my alliance
with Grand Tutor Li.

00:06:04.760 --> 00:06:06.600 line:80%
Those two old schemers…

00:06:06.680 --> 00:06:09.160 line:80%
It's always either
one side wins or the other.

00:06:10.080 --> 00:06:12.320 line:80%
When will someone else show up
and give me a break?

00:06:19.480 --> 00:06:21.240 line:80%
Master, what did His Majesty say?

00:06:21.320 --> 00:06:23.680 line:80%
That useless Qi Sheng,

00:06:23.760 --> 00:06:26.600 line:80%
a fence-sitter. He's flipped again.

00:06:26.680 --> 00:06:27.520 line:80%
It's…

00:06:31.040 --> 00:06:32.600 line:80%
With Xie Zheng back,

00:06:32.680 --> 00:06:35.960 line:80%
Wei Yan's gained more leverage.

00:06:37.000 --> 00:06:39.480 line:80%
Looks like His Majesty
is no one to count on.

00:06:40.120 --> 00:06:41.280 line:80%
Our Li family

00:06:42.240 --> 00:06:44.320 line:80%
needs to find another way.

00:06:47.680 --> 00:06:48.520 line:80%
Master,

00:06:49.440 --> 00:06:51.520 line:80%
Qi Min is likely to make a big move soon.

00:06:52.240 --> 00:06:55.960 line:80%
Also, the Chancellor's investigation
into Jinzhou has a lead.

00:06:56.040 --> 00:06:57.160 line:80%
SUI YUANQING HAS THE TIGER TALLY. KEY
TO JINZHOU CASE AND WEI QILIN’S INJUSTICE

00:06:57.240 --> 00:06:59.120 line:80%
Word came from Chongzhou.

00:06:59.840 --> 00:07:02.680 line:80%
Should we inform the young master?

00:07:06.720 --> 00:07:08.240 line:80%
Seventeen years ago,

00:07:08.320 --> 00:07:11.680 line:80%
the tiger tally Wei Qilin brought
to mobilize troops was real.

00:07:12.520 --> 00:07:15.680 line:80%
But to Prince Changxin, it became a fake.

00:07:16.640 --> 00:07:20.920 line:80%
Caught between that real and fake tally,

00:07:22.280 --> 00:07:24.800 line:80%
the key figure
is the man who delivered it,

00:07:30.560 --> 00:07:31.760 line:80%
Wei Qilin himself.

00:07:34.480 --> 00:07:35.920 line:80%
WEI MANOR

00:07:39.960 --> 00:07:44.000 line:80%
After all these days,
you finally dare to come back?

00:07:54.640 --> 00:07:55.800 line:80%
I heard Mother is ill.

00:07:56.640 --> 00:07:57.920 line:80%
I couldn't stop worrying.

00:08:03.280 --> 00:08:04.360 line:80%
As for Li Huaiqin's legs,

00:08:05.160 --> 00:08:06.320 line:80%
I alone am responsible.
I'll face the consequences myself.

00:08:06.400 --> 00:08:08.080 line:80%
Face it yourself?

00:08:09.560 --> 00:08:10.880 line:80%
You think you're worthy

00:08:11.720 --> 00:08:12.640 line:80%
of upholding the Wei family's honor?

00:08:14.600 --> 00:08:15.840 line:80%
You think you can?

00:08:20.240 --> 00:08:23.240 line:80%
The official matter,
I've already handled it.

00:08:24.360 --> 00:08:27.800 line:80%
But you won't escape
the family discipline.

00:08:29.600 --> 00:08:31.560 line:80%
-Guards.
-Here.

00:08:33.719 --> 00:08:35.719 line:80%
12, 13,

00:08:36.479 --> 00:08:38.479 line:80%
14, 15,

00:08:39.080 --> 00:08:40.080 line:80%
16,

00:08:40.599 --> 00:08:41.520 line:80%
17,

00:08:42.040 --> 00:08:42.880 line:80%
18.

00:08:43.760 --> 00:08:44.600 line:80%
Punishment complete.

00:08:47.680 --> 00:08:48.680 line:80%
Father,

00:08:50.720 --> 00:08:52.240 line:80%
Mother is ill.

00:08:53.680 --> 00:08:55.520 line:80%
Won't you go and stay with her?

00:08:56.280 --> 00:08:58.960 line:80%
I've already sent
for the imperial physician.

00:08:59.040 --> 00:09:02.200 line:80%
Do you know why I broke
Li Huaiqin's legs that day?

00:09:03.400 --> 00:09:04.640 line:80%
He insulted me.

00:09:05.600 --> 00:09:08.080 line:80%
He said I'm not your son.

00:09:08.960 --> 00:09:11.080 line:80%
Said your true love is that
childhood sweetheart in the palace.

00:09:11.960 --> 00:09:13.040 line:80%
My mother

00:09:13.760 --> 00:09:17.680 line:80%
has served you all these years,
given you everything.

00:09:17.760 --> 00:09:21.800 line:80%
And now she lies ill in bed,
and you won't even look at your own wife?

00:09:24.760 --> 00:09:25.680 line:80%
Chancellor,

00:09:26.880 --> 00:09:27.840 line:80%
a letter from Wei Sheng.

00:09:27.920 --> 00:09:30.000 line:80%
It concerns the Marquis of Wu'an.

00:09:35.960 --> 00:09:37.200 line:80%
See?

00:09:38.440 --> 00:09:40.160 line:80%
I have official matters to attend to.

00:09:41.840 --> 00:09:43.360 line:80%
As for your mother,

00:09:43.880 --> 00:09:45.120 line:80%
take good care of her.

00:09:45.840 --> 00:09:48.440 line:80%
If there's nothing else, stay put.

00:09:48.520 --> 00:09:49.520 line:80%
Don't wander around.

00:09:50.040 --> 00:09:52.240 line:80%
You only care for Xie Zheng.

00:09:53.240 --> 00:09:55.880 line:80%
Have you ever treated
me and Mother as family?

00:09:58.760 --> 00:09:59.880 line:80%
Am I right?

00:10:01.120 --> 00:10:05.080 line:80%
You care for Xie Zheng like he's your own,

00:10:05.680 --> 00:10:07.960 line:80%
pour all your energy, all your thoughts,

00:10:08.040 --> 00:10:10.640 line:80%
into him alone.

00:10:11.760 --> 00:10:12.880 line:80%
And me?

00:10:12.960 --> 00:10:16.000 line:80%
I can only stand by and watch.

00:10:21.440 --> 00:10:23.920 line:80%
Have you ever really looked at me?

00:10:25.000 --> 00:10:26.360 line:80%
Once?

00:10:26.440 --> 00:10:27.880 line:80%
Even once?

00:10:28.720 --> 00:10:31.920 line:80%
What I hate most
is this cold indifference of yours.

00:10:32.000 --> 00:10:34.360 line:80%
Since I was a child, no matter what I did,

00:10:34.440 --> 00:10:36.160 line:80%
you never cared.

00:10:37.000 --> 00:10:39.760 line:80%
Is Xie Zheng your son, or am I?

00:10:39.840 --> 00:10:42.200 line:80%
Am I some bastard
you picked up off the street?

00:10:42.280 --> 00:10:43.200 line:80%
Am I?

00:11:35.720 --> 00:11:38.160 line:80%
You're not a child anymore.

00:12:03.760 --> 00:12:05.880 line:80%
The Grand Princess has arrived.

00:12:06.600 --> 00:12:08.040 line:80%
Your Highness,

00:12:08.120 --> 00:12:09.840 line:80%
His Majesty is occupied
with state affairs.

00:12:09.920 --> 00:12:13.760 line:80%
Please calm down. I couldn't stop her.

00:12:16.360 --> 00:12:17.240 line:80%
Never mind.

00:12:17.320 --> 00:12:19.360 line:80%
I didn't expect you to stop her anyway.
You may go.

00:12:19.960 --> 00:12:21.000 line:80%
As you command.

00:12:22.440 --> 00:12:25.240 line:80%
I hear my royal brother wants to grant me
in marriage to the Marquis of Wu'an.

00:12:29.560 --> 00:12:33.560 line:80%
Sister, I found you
a legendary hero for a husband.

00:12:33.640 --> 00:12:34.840 line:80%
Why aren't you pleased?

00:12:37.960 --> 00:12:39.040 line:80%
I'll kill you!

00:12:39.120 --> 00:12:40.280 line:80%
-Stop hitting me, Sister!
-Stand still.

00:12:40.360 --> 00:12:41.280 line:80%
It hurts.

00:12:41.880 --> 00:12:43.600 line:80%
But Sister, didn't you use to say
you admired the Marquis of Wu'an?

00:12:43.680 --> 00:12:44.960 line:80%
That you wanted to marry him?

00:12:45.920 --> 00:12:48.440 line:80%
I was only six years old then.
Six years old!

00:12:49.080 --> 00:12:50.200 line:80%
-You just want the Marquis on your side.
-Sister…

00:12:50.280 --> 00:12:51.200 line:80%
-Stop hitting me.
-Using my marriage as an excuse.

00:12:51.280 --> 00:12:52.280 line:80%
Keep this up, and it won't be pretty.

00:12:52.360 --> 00:12:54.080 line:80%
So you do care about appearances?

00:12:55.320 --> 00:12:56.600 line:80%
First, you try to sell me off
to the Li family,

00:12:56.680 --> 00:12:58.400 line:80%
now to the Xie family.

00:12:58.480 --> 00:12:59.760 line:80%
Am I still the Grand Princess or not?

00:12:59.840 --> 00:13:01.400 line:80%
Do I have any dignity left?

00:13:01.480 --> 00:13:03.600 line:80%
I need my dignity too, Sister.

00:13:03.680 --> 00:13:04.800 line:80%
You're also a Qi.

00:13:04.880 --> 00:13:07.440 line:80%
Can you really stand by and watch
those two old dogs push me around?

00:13:14.920 --> 00:13:17.000 line:80%
I've lived in fear

00:13:17.840 --> 00:13:20.960 line:80%
for 17 years, Sister.

00:13:21.720 --> 00:13:25.200 line:80%
Sister, have you ever read

00:13:25.280 --> 00:13:29.960 line:80%
of such a pathetic emperor
in all the books?

00:13:32.200 --> 00:13:33.640 line:80%
Xie Zheng isn't Wei Yan.

00:13:34.520 --> 00:13:36.320 line:80%
Even without marriage as a favor,

00:13:36.840 --> 00:13:38.280 line:80%
he could still serve you, Brother.

00:13:38.960 --> 00:13:40.720 line:80%
Then… can you…

00:13:41.440 --> 00:13:43.080 line:80%
vouch for him forever, Sister?

00:13:44.320 --> 00:13:45.320 line:80%
Prince Changxin,

00:13:45.400 --> 00:13:47.120 line:80%
17 years ago,

00:13:47.200 --> 00:13:49.480 line:80%
he never imagined he'd rebel.

00:13:50.840 --> 00:13:54.280 line:80%
Everyone thought his family,
all of them, were dead.

00:13:54.360 --> 00:13:56.480 line:80%
And now suddenly there's this

00:13:56.560 --> 00:13:59.320 line:80%
Sui Yuanhuai faking his death
and escaping?

00:14:05.760 --> 00:14:08.520 line:80%
Anyway, Brother, stop playing matchmaker.

00:14:08.600 --> 00:14:10.120 line:80%
Or I'll be back.

00:14:10.200 --> 00:14:12.040 line:80%
This military training,

00:14:12.560 --> 00:14:15.160 line:80%
I may not have learned much else,
but warfare?

00:14:15.760 --> 00:14:17.360 line:80%
I've got it down pretty well.

00:14:17.440 --> 00:14:20.120 line:80%
I hear you. You've scared me enough.

00:14:33.680 --> 00:14:35.760 line:80%
Quick. Fetch Li Xiang.

00:14:36.360 --> 00:14:37.280 line:80%
Now.

00:14:37.360 --> 00:14:39.880 line:80%
Losing one ear won't kill him.

00:14:42.280 --> 00:14:44.360 line:80%
WEI MANOR

00:14:48.880 --> 00:14:50.640 line:80%
BY IMPERIAL GRACE

00:15:02.960 --> 00:15:04.920 line:80%
Chancellor, please save me.

00:15:05.000 --> 00:15:06.200 line:80%
Someone wants to depose me.

00:15:13.480 --> 00:15:14.480 line:80%
Chancellor,

00:15:15.160 --> 00:15:16.800 line:80%
from now on, I'll be obedient.

00:15:17.480 --> 00:15:21.120 line:80%
Everything before,
I was misled by the Li family.

00:15:32.120 --> 00:15:33.280 line:80%
-Chancellor?
-Your Majesty.

00:15:33.360 --> 00:15:34.720 line:80%
-Chancellor.
-Your Majesty.

00:15:34.800 --> 00:15:36.600 line:80%
You are the Son of Heaven, Your Majesty.

00:15:36.680 --> 00:15:38.920 line:80%
You should comport yourself as such.

00:15:39.440 --> 00:15:40.920 line:80%
How can you lose your composure like this?

00:15:51.360 --> 00:15:53.800 line:80%
Are rebel forces at the gates?

00:15:53.880 --> 00:15:57.480 line:80%
Is someone plotting to force the throne?

00:15:59.080 --> 00:15:59.920 line:80%
No to both.

00:16:01.920 --> 00:16:04.160 line:80%
The palace still stands.
The walls are intact.

00:16:04.680 --> 00:16:07.840 line:80%
Why such fear, Your Majesty?

00:16:10.280 --> 00:16:13.200 line:80%
Yes, I lost my composure.

00:16:24.560 --> 00:16:28.280 line:80%
Li Xiang returned from Jizhou, saying
there are rumors spreading in the army.

00:16:28.800 --> 00:16:30.560 line:80%
Someone from
the former Eastern Palace appeared.

00:16:33.680 --> 00:16:37.000 line:80%
Seventeen years ago,
you ensured I took the throne.

00:16:37.080 --> 00:16:39.520 line:80%
I know that in this world,

00:16:40.040 --> 00:16:42.560 line:80%
only you will always stand with me.

00:16:43.080 --> 00:16:45.360 line:80%
You're the only one I trust.

00:16:58.080 --> 00:16:59.160 line:80%
Your Majesty.

00:17:02.680 --> 00:17:03.680 line:80%
Chancellor.

00:17:05.000 --> 00:17:07.320 line:80%
I'm truly unsettled. My heart is racing.

00:17:08.680 --> 00:17:11.119 line:80%
Rumors about the former Eastern Palace

00:17:11.200 --> 00:17:13.200 line:80%
have surfaced several times
over the past decade.

00:17:13.879 --> 00:17:15.360 line:80%
I'll handle them.

00:17:16.440 --> 00:17:17.320 line:80%
But Your Majesty,

00:17:18.080 --> 00:17:20.280 line:80%
you received the throne
through abdication from the late emperor,

00:17:20.360 --> 00:17:23.080 line:80%
in full legitimacy.

00:17:23.960 --> 00:17:25.840 line:80%
What is there to fear?

00:17:27.399 --> 00:17:29.360 line:80%
Your Majesty must not forget,

00:17:29.440 --> 00:17:30.960 line:80%
in the northwest,

00:17:31.480 --> 00:17:34.400 line:80%
there is a newly risen general
of great merit

00:17:34.920 --> 00:17:37.960 line:80%
who saved the people
from suffering and won their hearts.

00:17:38.040 --> 00:17:39.160 line:80%
You should

00:17:39.840 --> 00:17:41.840 line:80%
seize this chance to win this person over.

00:17:41.920 --> 00:17:44.720 line:80%
Only then can you secure
the people's trust

00:17:45.320 --> 00:17:47.680 line:80%
and demonstrate your imperial authority.

00:17:48.360 --> 00:17:51.240 line:80%
You mean that pig-slaughtering woman,
Fan Changyu?

00:17:55.840 --> 00:17:58.400 line:80%
She does have some courage and strength,

00:17:58.480 --> 00:18:01.120 line:80%
and she did kill Prince Changxin
on the battlefield.

00:18:01.760 --> 00:18:05.320 line:80%
But she's of low birth,
with no roots or connections at court.

00:18:05.400 --> 00:18:07.040 line:80%
How could she serve me?

00:18:07.560 --> 00:18:08.880 line:80%
Don't forget.

00:18:08.960 --> 00:18:12.920 line:80%
That woman holds command
over half the Jizhou army.

00:18:13.000 --> 00:18:15.520 line:80%
She's also someone
the Li family is trying to win over.

00:18:16.040 --> 00:18:19.560 line:80%
If you summon her to court now,
while her merits pile up,

00:18:19.640 --> 00:18:22.440 line:80%
and honor her properly,

00:18:23.600 --> 00:18:27.320 line:80%
it shows your favor.

00:18:30.360 --> 00:18:32.280 line:80%
Excellent. Very well.

00:18:32.920 --> 00:18:35.240 line:80%
I'll follow the Chancellor's counsel.

00:18:35.320 --> 00:18:36.240 line:80%
Quickly issue my decree.

00:18:36.320 --> 00:18:39.000 line:80%
Summon Fan Changyu and all meritorious
officers who helped quell the rebellion

00:18:39.080 --> 00:18:40.120 line:80%
to the capital immediately
to receive their titles.

00:18:40.200 --> 00:18:42.960 line:80%
Our dynasty's first
formidable female general,

00:18:43.040 --> 00:18:45.280 line:80%
I will personally preside
over their investiture ceremony.

00:18:45.360 --> 00:18:47.160 line:80%
Your Majesty is truly wise.

00:18:53.960 --> 00:18:57.280 line:80%
The Qis are all liars, just as despicable.

00:18:58.400 --> 00:18:59.520 line:80%
Be careful, Chancellor.

00:19:00.480 --> 00:19:03.880 line:80%
Even the emperor knows
about the former Eastern Palace now.

00:19:05.120 --> 00:19:07.600 line:80%
Is he planning to leave it open?

00:19:11.840 --> 00:19:13.400 line:80%
Is Xie Jiuheng…

00:19:15.040 --> 00:19:17.920 line:80%
trying to become the second Wei Yan?

00:19:29.840 --> 00:19:31.960 line:80%
By imperial decree.

00:19:32.040 --> 00:19:35.080 line:80%
"The rebel prince Changxin raised
insurrection in the western frontier.

00:19:35.160 --> 00:19:38.480 line:80%
The female general Fan Changyu, with
loyalty and courage, vanquished the enemy

00:19:38.560 --> 00:19:40.600 line:80%
and cut down
the rebel leader on the battlefield.

00:19:40.680 --> 00:19:42.360 line:80%
I commend her merit

00:19:42.440 --> 00:19:45.520 line:80%
and specially appoint her
as Flower-Adorned General,

00:19:45.600 --> 00:19:47.480 line:80%
rank fourth,

00:19:47.560 --> 00:19:49.400 line:80%
and bestow upon her
the purple and gold fish pouch.

00:19:49.480 --> 00:19:52.320 line:80%
She is hereby ordered
to present herself at the capital

00:19:52.400 --> 00:19:54.440 line:80%
for an audience
and receive her investiture."

00:19:58.560 --> 00:20:00.000 line:80%
So this is the capital.

00:20:00.080 --> 00:20:03.160 line:80%
Look at these buildings,
these streets, all these people.

00:20:03.240 --> 00:20:04.440 line:80%
Cang, quick, pinch me.

00:20:04.520 --> 00:20:05.760 line:80%
Am I dreaming?

00:20:06.280 --> 00:20:08.320 line:80%
Ow. Not dreaming.

00:20:08.400 --> 00:20:09.400 line:80%
All of you, mind yourselves.

00:20:09.480 --> 00:20:11.960 line:80%
Don't let anyone figure out
we're from the countryside.

00:20:12.560 --> 00:20:13.840 line:80%
So what if we're from the country?

00:20:14.880 --> 00:20:16.280 line:80%
Fan earned her rank

00:20:16.360 --> 00:20:19.120 line:80%
with a pig-slaughtering blade
out in the sticks.

00:20:19.200 --> 00:20:20.520 line:80%
Who dares look down on her?

00:20:24.720 --> 00:20:27.240 line:20%
Look at our female general, so commanding.

00:20:27.320 --> 00:20:30.000 line:20%
If General Fan were a man,
I'd seek out a marriage.

00:20:30.080 --> 00:20:32.280 line:80%
Maybe she's got a brother.

00:20:32.360 --> 00:20:34.520 line:80%
If I can't marry her,
being her sister-in-law would be nice too.

00:20:34.600 --> 00:20:38.120 line:80%
Never thought she'd look even handsomer
on horseback than any young lad.

00:20:38.200 --> 00:20:41.960 line:80%
I hear His Majesty is hosting
the investiture ceremony himself.

00:20:42.040 --> 00:20:42.880 line:80%
Really?

00:20:42.960 --> 00:20:45.400 line:80%
-General Fan, formidable!
-General Fan!

00:20:45.920 --> 00:20:46.840 line:80%
General Fan!

00:21:51.080 --> 00:21:53.080 line:80%
By His Majesty's decree,

00:21:53.160 --> 00:21:56.640 line:80%
summon Li Huai'an,
Military Administrator of Jizhou,

00:21:56.720 --> 00:22:01.920 line:80%
and Fan Changyu,
Flower-Adorned General, to an audience.

00:22:08.120 --> 00:22:09.120 line:80%
DILIGENT IN RULE, DEVOTED TO THE WORTHY

00:22:20.640 --> 00:22:23.600 line:80%
-Long live the Emperor!
-Long live the Emperor!

00:22:24.840 --> 00:22:25.920 line:80%
Rise, my loyal ministers.

00:22:26.440 --> 00:22:27.480 line:80%
Thank you, Your Majesty.

00:22:29.760 --> 00:22:32.280 line:80%
Take a look, my ministers.

00:22:33.200 --> 00:22:36.240 line:80%
These are the backbone of our Dayin.

00:22:45.280 --> 00:22:46.520 line:80%
I dare not accept such praise.

00:22:47.440 --> 00:22:49.960 line:80%
Loyal service to Your Majesty
is a subject's duty.

00:22:50.600 --> 00:22:52.760 line:80%
Moreover, in this campaign,

00:22:52.840 --> 00:22:55.840 line:80%
the greatest credit belongs to General He
and the Marquis of Wu'an.

00:22:56.560 --> 00:23:00.720 line:80%
General He and the Marquis of Wu'an
are indeed pillars of Dayin.

00:23:03.120 --> 00:23:04.920 line:80%
My heart aches deeply

00:23:05.800 --> 00:23:07.560 line:80%
over General He's death at Lucheng.

00:23:07.640 --> 00:23:09.320 line:80%
I've barely eaten for days.

00:23:10.240 --> 00:23:13.000 line:80%
Thankfully, Dayin has the Marquis of Wu'an

00:23:13.080 --> 00:23:15.280 line:80%
and loyal ministers like you,

00:23:15.360 --> 00:23:19.400 line:80%
so I and all of you can rest easy.

00:23:20.640 --> 00:23:23.080 line:80%
I will not fail
Your Majesty's expectations.

00:23:23.960 --> 00:23:28.240 line:80%
I hear a female general has emerged
from among our people.

00:23:28.320 --> 00:23:30.000 line:80%
Step forward and let me see you.

00:23:32.520 --> 00:23:35.600 line:80%
Commander Fan Changyu
pays her respects to Your Majesty.

00:23:36.400 --> 00:23:37.520 line:80%
Closer.

00:23:45.800 --> 00:23:48.280 line:80%
Commander Fan Changyu
pays her respects to Your Majesty.

00:23:50.800 --> 00:23:52.040 line:80%
Raise your head.

00:23:55.480 --> 00:23:57.480 line:80%
A true iron-willed peony.

00:24:01.120 --> 00:24:02.480 line:80%
Are you married, General?

00:24:04.120 --> 00:24:06.520 line:80%
To answer Your Majesty,
I already have a husband.

00:24:09.080 --> 00:24:10.840 line:80%
Then where is your husband now?

00:24:12.800 --> 00:24:14.360 line:80%
When conscription began earlier this year,

00:24:14.440 --> 00:24:16.040 line:80%
my husband went to the front.

00:24:17.080 --> 00:24:18.840 line:80%
Eager to find him,

00:24:18.920 --> 00:24:20.400 line:80%
I ended up joining the army myself
along the way.

00:24:21.120 --> 00:24:23.160 line:80%
But the Battle of Lucheng was so brutal.

00:24:23.680 --> 00:24:26.800 line:80%
To this day, I don't know
if he's alive or dead.

00:24:26.880 --> 00:24:28.360 line:80%
Alive or dead, you say?

00:24:28.440 --> 00:24:29.920 line:80%
Then perhaps, General, you might--

00:24:42.200 --> 00:24:43.960 line:80%
In my 17 years on the throne,

00:24:44.040 --> 00:24:46.600 line:80%
this is the first time
I've seen a female general.

00:24:47.120 --> 00:24:48.840 line:80%
I was momentarily overcome just now.

00:24:50.560 --> 00:24:52.200 line:80%
Minister Fan, in quelling the rebellion,

00:24:52.280 --> 00:24:55.000 line:80%
you first killed Shi Hu,
then beheaded Prince Changxin.

00:24:55.080 --> 00:24:57.560 line:80%
Truly, your contributions
cannot be overlooked.

00:24:57.640 --> 00:25:00.600 line:80%
I hereby specially appoint you
as Flower-Adorned General,

00:25:00.680 --> 00:25:02.240 line:80%
with the added honor
of Fourth-Rank Noble Lady.

00:25:10.960 --> 00:25:13.760 line:80%
Commander Fan Changyu thanks Your Majesty
for your boundless grace.

00:25:21.200 --> 00:25:22.080 line:80%
Your Majesty,

00:25:22.160 --> 00:25:24.600 line:80%
since the founding of Dayin,

00:25:24.680 --> 00:25:28.480 line:80%
there has never been a female general
holding rank above five.

00:25:29.320 --> 00:25:31.760 line:80%
Appointing a Flower-Adorned General
is already without precedent,

00:25:31.840 --> 00:25:33.920 line:80%
-let alone
-Seems the Grand Tutor's faction

00:25:34.000 --> 00:25:36.480 line:80%
-half of the command in the northwest.
-is still clinging to half the army.

00:25:36.560 --> 00:25:38.400 line:80%
Your Majesty, I urge you to reconsider.

00:25:44.880 --> 00:25:45.720 line:80%
Reporting to Your Majesty.

00:25:46.320 --> 00:25:48.000 line:80%
General Fan is unlike any ordinary woman.

00:25:48.080 --> 00:25:50.280 line:80%
She took Prince Changxin's head and
single-handedly turned the tide of battle.

00:25:50.920 --> 00:25:53.040 line:80%
-She deserves the highest credit.
-Military Administrator Li,

00:25:54.320 --> 00:25:57.840 line:80%
mind your words before His Majesty.

00:25:59.080 --> 00:26:03.280 line:80%
I hear that before joining the army,
General Fan

00:26:03.360 --> 00:26:06.600 line:80%
was a pig-slaughtering woman
from some remote border town.

00:26:07.120 --> 00:26:08.960 line:80%
But how could that be?

00:26:09.040 --> 00:26:12.480 line:80%
To kill the formidable Prince Changxin,

00:26:13.120 --> 00:26:16.520 line:80%
-surely not--
-I thank Grand Tutor Li for the praise.

00:26:17.040 --> 00:26:21.240 line:80%
As a rustic woman, I know nothing else,

00:26:21.320 --> 00:26:25.000 line:80%
only that pork must be butchered clean,

00:26:25.080 --> 00:26:26.920 line:80%
and enemies must be cut down hard.

00:26:28.640 --> 00:26:32.560 line:80%
General Fan, this is not
your filthy pig-slaughtering pen.

00:26:32.640 --> 00:26:35.480 line:80%
Now that you hold an official title,

00:26:35.560 --> 00:26:38.240 line:80%
you must mind your words
and conduct at all times,

00:26:38.320 --> 00:26:40.160 line:80%
especially here in court,

00:26:40.240 --> 00:26:43.640 line:80%
especially before His Majesty
and the Grand Tutor.

00:26:43.720 --> 00:26:45.760 line:80%
You speak well.

00:26:46.920 --> 00:26:47.920 line:80%
Speaking of pigsties,

00:26:48.600 --> 00:26:51.160 line:80%
I keep mine spotless,

00:26:51.240 --> 00:26:52.240 line:80%
and my pigs are fat and healthy.

00:26:52.840 --> 00:26:54.240 line:80%
But there are always some rotten pigs

00:26:54.320 --> 00:26:57.360 line:80%
that insist on pissing
and shitting everywhere.

00:26:57.440 --> 00:26:59.880 line:80%
No matter how clean the place,
it ends up filthy.

00:26:59.960 --> 00:27:00.800 line:80%
It's…

00:27:04.160 --> 00:27:05.840 line:80%
Who are you calling a pig?

00:27:05.920 --> 00:27:08.200 line:80%
Don't be upset, Minister.
I didn't say you were a pig.

00:27:10.320 --> 00:27:11.520 line:80%
General Fan is quite amusing.

00:27:12.040 --> 00:27:15.560 line:80%
Her words may be blunt,
but they carry some truth.

00:27:18.440 --> 00:27:22.120 line:80%
General Fan, sharp words
are no substitute for battle merits.

00:27:22.200 --> 00:27:23.080 line:80%
As a military officer,

00:27:23.680 --> 00:27:26.120 line:80%
your duty is to protect the realm,

00:27:26.720 --> 00:27:29.920 line:80%
not to spar with words here.

00:27:30.000 --> 00:27:32.360 line:80%
Grand Tutor Li speaks well.

00:27:32.440 --> 00:27:34.640 line:80%
I certainly know the importance
of protecting the realm.

00:27:36.120 --> 00:27:39.240 line:80%
But when the border folk were suffering,

00:27:39.320 --> 00:27:41.240 line:80%
where were you with your smug remarks?

00:27:42.240 --> 00:27:43.080 line:80%
You…

00:27:45.240 --> 00:27:46.480 line:80%
Enough.

00:27:48.080 --> 00:27:50.200 line:80%
General Fan's forthright nature
is truly refreshing,

00:27:50.800 --> 00:27:53.040 line:80%
quite unlike ordinary women.

00:27:54.520 --> 00:27:57.560 line:80%
No wonder she's earned
such illustrious battle merits.

00:27:57.640 --> 00:28:01.400 line:80%
As they say, a hero's origins matter not.

00:28:01.480 --> 00:28:07.560 line:80%
We court officials
should show her some leniency.

00:28:09.200 --> 00:28:12.880 line:80%
As for the military command,
we can discuss it another day.

00:28:15.840 --> 00:28:18.080 line:80%
Thank you, Chancellor Wei.

00:28:18.800 --> 00:28:20.360 line:80%
I stand here today

00:28:21.240 --> 00:28:24.200 line:80%
thanks to your generosity.

00:28:29.840 --> 00:28:32.640 line:80%
But I don't see this as mere wordplay.

00:28:33.560 --> 00:28:36.560 line:80%
Court is like butchering.
Both require rules.

00:28:36.640 --> 00:28:38.760 line:80%
Butchering demands a clean kill.

00:28:38.840 --> 00:28:40.880 line:80%
Speaking in court
demands hitting the mark.

00:28:40.960 --> 00:28:43.760 line:80%
All these twists and turns,
how can they solve anything?

00:28:43.840 --> 00:28:45.800 line:80%
Take the Battle of Lucheng.

00:28:45.880 --> 00:28:48.320 line:80%
If the soldiers had all hung back,

00:28:48.400 --> 00:28:50.040 line:80%
who would have held the city?

00:28:50.120 --> 00:28:53.240 line:80%
General Fan's words
are reasonable point by point,

00:28:53.840 --> 00:28:56.360 line:80%
just lacking in decorum.

00:28:56.440 --> 00:29:00.840 line:80%
You must study proper etiquette
from now on.

00:29:00.920 --> 00:29:02.680 line:80%
The Chancellor speaks truly.

00:29:02.760 --> 00:29:05.560 line:80%
My habit of speaking bluntly
really does need correcting.

00:29:06.720 --> 00:29:07.640 line:80%
Oh,

00:29:07.720 --> 00:29:11.240 line:80%
and the Marquis asked me to pay respects
at his parents' graves for him.

00:29:15.880 --> 00:29:18.920 line:80%
Chancellor, would you like
to pay respects to your sister

00:29:19.000 --> 00:29:20.280 line:80%
and General Xie as well?

00:29:36.960 --> 00:29:39.320 line:80%
If there's no further business, Ministers,

00:29:40.160 --> 00:29:41.040 line:80%
you may withdraw.

00:29:41.720 --> 00:29:46.280 line:80%
Speak if you have business.
If not, this court is dismissed.

00:29:47.080 --> 00:29:49.320 line:80%
We respectfully see His Majesty off.

00:30:06.960 --> 00:30:08.440 line:80%
<i>Nice place.</i>

00:30:09.040 --> 00:30:10.520 line:80%
<i>Not many nice people.</i>

00:30:11.520 --> 00:30:13.440 line:80%
<i>Nowhere near as good as Lin'an.</i>

00:30:17.840 --> 00:30:18.680 line:80%
General Fan,

00:30:21.920 --> 00:30:23.200 line:80%
you shouldn't make
so many enemies at court.

00:30:28.120 --> 00:30:29.440 line:80%
Grandfather.

00:30:32.720 --> 00:30:34.840 line:80%
So you do remember I'm your grandfather.

00:30:35.840 --> 00:30:36.880 line:80%
Go home.

00:30:43.720 --> 00:30:45.680 line:80%
General Fan, please wait.

00:30:48.400 --> 00:30:50.120 line:80%
I'm not your grandson.

00:30:50.200 --> 00:30:51.960 line:80%
What? you want to lecture me too?

00:30:53.840 --> 00:30:56.920 line:80%
General Fan,
your performance in court today

00:30:57.000 --> 00:30:59.360 line:80%
left quite an impression.

00:30:59.440 --> 00:31:01.960 line:80%
Now that you've earned
His Majesty's praise,

00:31:02.040 --> 00:31:04.560 line:80%
everyone hails you
as a heroine among women.

00:31:04.640 --> 00:31:06.840 line:80%
But as a woman,

00:31:06.920 --> 00:31:09.640 line:80%
you'll marry and bear children
sooner or later.

00:31:09.720 --> 00:31:11.640 line:80%
No matter how great your merits,

00:31:11.720 --> 00:31:13.560 line:80%
this is as far as you'll go.

00:31:14.600 --> 00:31:17.160 line:80%
A sparrow can never reach the high branch.

00:31:17.240 --> 00:31:19.440 line:80%
It will never become a phoenix.

00:31:20.480 --> 00:31:23.840 line:80%
Women can marry, bear children,
and still earn merits.

00:31:24.520 --> 00:31:26.600 line:80%
Besides, what's it to you?

00:31:27.840 --> 00:31:29.680 line:80%
General Fan, have you heard the saying,

00:31:29.760 --> 00:31:32.680 line:80%
"A wise man submits to circumstances?"

00:31:34.560 --> 00:31:35.480 line:80%
Fine.

00:31:36.320 --> 00:31:38.520 line:80%
I will now wisely take my leave.

00:31:55.600 --> 00:31:56.720 line:80%
Master.

00:31:57.240 --> 00:31:59.320 line:80%
Grand Tutor, nice palanquin.

00:32:00.720 --> 00:32:01.560 line:80%
Master.

00:32:06.160 --> 00:32:07.600 line:80%
Pride comes before a fall.

00:32:08.120 --> 00:32:11.680 line:80%
She'll trip up sooner or later.

00:32:16.560 --> 00:32:18.520 line:80%
LONGQING GATE

00:32:25.040 --> 00:32:26.640 line:80%
-Master.
-Grand Tutor.

00:32:26.720 --> 00:32:28.120 line:80%
Master, are you alright?

00:32:29.720 --> 00:32:31.840 line:80%
-Master.
-Fan Changyu…

00:32:33.440 --> 00:32:35.240 line:80%
Just you wait.

00:32:39.680 --> 00:32:42.560 line:80%
Chancellor Wei collapses in anger.
Grand Tutor Li tumbles from his palanquin.

00:32:42.640 --> 00:32:44.720 line:80%
The Grand Princess has arrived.

00:32:45.600 --> 00:32:46.640 line:80%
Sister.

00:32:46.720 --> 00:32:47.800 line:80%
Sister.

00:32:49.000 --> 00:32:50.360 line:80%
What's all the joy about?

00:32:51.120 --> 00:32:53.760 line:80%
You… Do you know
General Fan came to court today?

00:32:53.840 --> 00:32:55.680 line:80%
She's truly an extraordinary person.

00:32:55.760 --> 00:32:56.680 line:80%
Let me tell you, Sister,

00:32:56.760 --> 00:33:00.000 line:80%
since I ascended the throne,
I've never laughed so freely as today.

00:33:00.080 --> 00:33:01.800 line:80%
Tell me. What kind of person is she?

00:33:02.560 --> 00:33:03.920 line:80%
Changyu…

00:33:04.600 --> 00:33:08.160 line:80%
Changyu is forthright and honest,
simple and lovely.

00:33:08.240 --> 00:33:09.240 line:80%
Her martial skill is exceptional.

00:33:09.840 --> 00:33:12.640 line:80%
She is utterly sincere with friends,
willing to die for her comrades,

00:33:12.720 --> 00:33:14.640 line:80%
and toward the Marquis of Wu'an,
she is even more…

00:33:17.160 --> 00:33:18.440 line:80%
Even more what toward
the Marquis of Wu'an?

00:33:19.840 --> 00:33:21.920 line:80%
<i>When you return to the capital, do not</i>
<i>reveal anything about Changyu and me.</i>

00:33:22.520 --> 00:33:23.960 line:80%
<i>Someone might seize on it</i>
<i>to stir up trouble.</i>

00:33:26.560 --> 00:33:28.120 line:80%
She holds him in high esteem.

00:33:28.200 --> 00:33:29.680 line:80%
They are comrades who fought side by side.

00:33:32.360 --> 00:33:35.600 line:80%
So she is not only formidable in battle,
she can also influence Xie Zheng.

00:33:36.120 --> 00:33:38.000 line:80%
I've been worrying about
having no one useful.

00:33:38.080 --> 00:33:39.200 line:80%
This woman suits me perfectly.

00:33:43.120 --> 00:33:44.040 line:80%
Grandfather,

00:33:44.560 --> 00:33:46.400 line:80%
though Qi Min is an imperial grandson,

00:33:46.920 --> 00:33:48.120 line:80%
he is no worthy ruler.

00:33:48.800 --> 00:33:51.640 line:80%
His nature is twisted,
his methods vicious.

00:33:52.320 --> 00:33:54.960 line:80%
If our Li family helps him reclaim power,

00:33:55.640 --> 00:33:57.040 line:80%
once he's in control,

00:33:58.360 --> 00:34:01.200 line:80%
that will be the beginning
of suffering for all the people.

00:34:01.280 --> 00:34:03.120 line:80%
Look at Qi Sheng now,

00:34:03.200 --> 00:34:04.760 line:80%
just a puppet of Wei Yan.

00:34:04.840 --> 00:34:06.840 line:80%
His virtue doesn't match his position.
His talent doesn't fit his role.

00:34:07.680 --> 00:34:09.160 line:80%
And Wei Yan's character…

00:34:09.680 --> 00:34:12.999 line:80%
I don't need to tell you.
You know it well.

00:34:13.959 --> 00:34:17.400 line:80%
In past campaigns, he showed
total disregard for the people's lives,

00:34:17.479 --> 00:34:19.200 line:80%
forcing grain levies

00:34:19.760 --> 00:34:22.280 line:80%
while the people starved, displaced,

00:34:22.360 --> 00:34:24.240 line:80%
dying in the streets.

00:34:24.320 --> 00:34:26.320 line:80%
That misery, all his doing.

00:34:26.400 --> 00:34:29.920 line:80%
That's what true cruelty looks like.

00:34:29.999 --> 00:34:33.439 line:80%
That's what really
makes the people suffer.

00:34:33.519 --> 00:34:35.600 line:80%
Qi Min's cruelty far exceeds Wei Yan's.

00:34:36.200 --> 00:34:37.760 line:80%
I saw it with my own eyes.

00:34:40.200 --> 00:34:41.120 line:80%
Grandfather.

00:34:42.439 --> 00:34:44.320 line:80%
Our Li family has served loyally
for generations.

00:34:45.479 --> 00:34:47.240 line:80%
We cannot aid a tyrant,

00:34:47.880 --> 00:34:50.880 line:80%
cannot let a man
of such vile character ascend the throne.

00:34:50.959 --> 00:34:53.280 line:80%
But he is Crown Prince Chengde's heir.

00:34:53.360 --> 00:34:55.640 line:80%
He carries the true bloodline
of the royal house.

00:34:55.720 --> 00:34:59.280 line:80%
All these years, wandering and suffering,

00:34:59.360 --> 00:35:01.680 line:80%
it's only natural
his nature became disordered.

00:35:02.280 --> 00:35:04.000 line:80%
You should understand.

00:35:04.080 --> 00:35:06.360 line:80%
Don't judge too hastily.

00:35:06.440 --> 00:35:08.160 line:80%
Grandfather, ever heard

00:35:08.240 --> 00:35:10.280 line:80%
of "killing the dog
once the game is caught"?

00:35:10.360 --> 00:35:12.360 line:80%
My boy,

00:35:13.320 --> 00:35:16.680 line:80%
your teacher He Jingyuan
had principles, upheld righteousness.

00:35:18.000 --> 00:35:20.520 line:80%
He was a first-rate hero of Dayin.

00:35:20.600 --> 00:35:24.040 line:80%
And he died on the battlefield.

00:35:24.560 --> 00:35:26.760 line:80%
In the end, it all came to nothing.

00:35:26.840 --> 00:35:28.760 line:80%
No matter how much
you talk about duty to the state,

00:35:28.840 --> 00:35:30.560 line:80%
what difference does it make?

00:35:31.760 --> 00:35:34.400 line:80%
Then you shouldn't have sent me
to the northwest in the first place.

00:35:36.040 --> 00:35:37.960 line:80%
I ask you to think clearly.

00:35:38.480 --> 00:35:42.200 line:80%
Is the current emperor
a wise ruler or a foolish one?

00:35:42.280 --> 00:35:46.120 line:80%
Does he benefit the realm or not?

00:36:03.360 --> 00:36:04.200 line:80%
Master.

00:36:06.400 --> 00:36:08.160 line:80%
Surround the study immediately.

00:36:08.240 --> 00:36:10.960 line:80%
If he dares act rashly,
detain him at once,

00:36:11.040 --> 00:36:12.080 line:80%
then report back.

00:36:12.800 --> 00:36:13.680 line:80%
Yes, sir.

00:36:14.520 --> 00:36:16.160 line:80%
Qi Min is settled.

00:36:16.240 --> 00:36:17.200 line:80%
He's at…

00:36:18.840 --> 00:36:22.440 line:20%
GUO'S TAVERN

00:36:22.520 --> 00:36:24.320 line:20%
JINGQUE HOUSE

00:36:26.040 --> 00:36:27.320 line:80%
Come here.

00:36:27.400 --> 00:36:29.080 line:80%
-Sir, what are you doing?
-Beauty…

00:36:29.160 --> 00:36:30.760 line:80%
Please don't, sir.

00:36:30.840 --> 00:36:32.000 line:80%
Where are you going?

00:36:32.800 --> 00:36:34.240 line:80%
We haven't finished our drinks.

00:36:34.320 --> 00:36:36.280 line:80%
Little lady, don't run. Little lady!

00:36:36.360 --> 00:36:37.280 line:80%
Sir.

00:36:38.960 --> 00:36:40.600 line:80%
General Fan, come join us.

00:36:40.680 --> 00:36:42.240 line:80%
Yeah, General Fan, come on in.

00:36:42.840 --> 00:36:44.480 line:80%
No, thanks. You enjoy yourselves.

00:36:45.360 --> 00:36:46.480 line:80%
It's…

00:36:46.560 --> 00:36:47.640 line:80%
Sir, come catch me.

00:36:47.720 --> 00:36:48.720 line:80%
Alright.

00:36:50.240 --> 00:36:52.280 line:80%
Socializing? What does that mean?

00:36:52.360 --> 00:36:55.480 line:80%
It's when you eat and drink
with a bunch of strangers,

00:36:55.560 --> 00:36:57.080 line:80%
and by the time you're done,
they're not strangers anymore.

00:36:57.160 --> 00:36:58.400 line:80%
How about socializing with me?

00:36:59.360 --> 00:37:00.200 line:80%
Right here, with me.

00:37:02.960 --> 00:37:03.880 line:80%
JINGQUE HOUSE

00:37:10.600 --> 00:37:11.960 line:80%
General Fan.

00:37:12.040 --> 00:37:14.320 line:80%
-General Fan, until we meet again.
-Until we meet again.

00:37:14.400 --> 00:37:15.640 line:80%
Until we meet again.

00:37:15.720 --> 00:37:18.200 line:80%
-Sir, let me see you out.
-Master, are you drunk?

00:37:18.280 --> 00:37:19.960 line:80%
-Come again next time.
-Definitely.

00:37:20.040 --> 00:37:22.080 line:80%
Remember to bring the bracelet
that you promised to me.

00:37:23.440 --> 00:37:25.320 line:80%
-Let's go, Fan?
-I'm going to take a stroll.

00:37:25.400 --> 00:37:26.240 line:80%
You all go ahead.

00:37:26.920 --> 00:37:28.040 line:80%
-Eh?
-Don't forget about me.

00:37:34.160 --> 00:37:35.080 line:80%
Coat.

00:37:36.680 --> 00:37:38.560 line:80%
You all wait here. I'll go check.

00:38:24.360 --> 00:38:25.200 line:80%
Why are you here?

00:38:27.080 --> 00:38:27.920 line:80%
I missed you.

00:38:56.320 --> 00:38:59.480 line:80%
ZHANG'S NOODLES

00:39:00.560 --> 00:39:02.240 line:80%
Aren't you afraid someone will see us?

00:39:02.320 --> 00:39:03.280 line:80%
So what if they do?

00:39:03.360 --> 00:39:05.680 line:80%
It's your first time to the capital.
I was worried about you.

00:39:06.640 --> 00:39:07.840 line:80%
But seeing

00:39:07.920 --> 00:39:10.720 line:80%
our Flower-Adorned General
handling things so smoothly,

00:39:10.800 --> 00:39:11.640 line:80%
I'm relieved.

00:39:17.440 --> 00:39:18.880 line:80%
Those officials,

00:39:19.400 --> 00:39:21.960 line:80%
none of them care about the truth
of 17 years ago anymore.

00:39:23.360 --> 00:39:25.480 line:80%
In the puppet plays,

00:39:25.560 --> 00:39:28.880 line:80%
when someone kneels
before the throne, gets justice,

00:39:28.960 --> 00:39:30.120 line:80%
good and evil punished,

00:39:30.640 --> 00:39:31.680 line:80%
all fake.

00:39:32.920 --> 00:39:34.160 line:80%
The emperor's no help either.

00:39:37.640 --> 00:39:38.640 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:39:39.360 --> 00:39:41.160 line:80%
I'll search for the truth with you.

00:39:43.480 --> 00:39:45.160 line:80%
We'll clear your father's name.

00:39:53.120 --> 00:39:54.000 line:80%
Thank you.

00:40:01.400 --> 00:40:03.640 line:80%
-Go home?
-Go home? Aren't we waiting for Changyu?

00:40:03.720 --> 00:40:06.160 line:80%
Didn't you say the capital's full of
bad people? Shouldn't we look out for her?

00:40:06.240 --> 00:40:07.080 line:80%
Right.

00:40:07.160 --> 00:40:09.800 line:80%
Today in court, the emperor
asked Changyu if she had a husband.

00:40:09.880 --> 00:40:10.880 line:80%
What's he up to?

00:40:11.440 --> 00:40:13.840 line:80%
That bastard emperor…
He definitely wants her in the palace.

00:40:13.920 --> 00:40:15.200 line:80%
What good could he possibly have in mind?

00:40:15.720 --> 00:40:16.600 line:80%
You're catching on.

00:40:17.640 --> 00:40:19.200 line:80%
You stop chattering.

00:40:20.480 --> 00:40:21.840 line:80%
With the Marquis of Wu'an around,

00:40:22.480 --> 00:40:24.160 line:80%
no one in this world can hurt her.

00:40:26.560 --> 00:40:28.120 line:80%
Worrying yourselves sick over nothing.

00:40:29.440 --> 00:40:31.120 line:80%
Pointless, completely pointless.

00:40:33.880 --> 00:40:34.880 line:80%
You go back.

00:40:35.880 --> 00:40:37.000 line:80%
I'll take my walk alone.

00:40:42.920 --> 00:40:44.520 line:80%
HUMBLE YOURSELF AND STAY ON GUARD

00:40:59.560 --> 00:41:01.120 line:80%
-I pay my respects to Your Majesty.
-I pay my respects to Your Majesty.

00:41:01.720 --> 00:41:04.480 line:80%
What brings both of you before me today?

00:41:05.560 --> 00:41:08.400 line:80%
Your Majesty, I have a memorial to submit.

00:41:08.480 --> 00:41:10.560 line:80%
That Flower-Adorned General, Fan Changyu,

00:41:10.640 --> 00:41:12.320 line:80%
behaves arrogantly
and oversteps her bounds.

00:41:12.400 --> 00:41:13.720 line:80%
She undermines
the very foundation of Dayin.

00:41:14.240 --> 00:41:16.160 line:80%
Not only did she defy Chancellor Wei,

00:41:16.240 --> 00:41:17.760 line:80%
she showed disrespect to me as well.

00:41:17.840 --> 00:41:20.440 line:80%
I request that Your Majesty
take appropriate action.

00:41:22.240 --> 00:41:24.720 line:80%
Chancellor Wei, you've also come
to impeach General Fan?

00:41:24.800 --> 00:41:26.480 line:80%
No, Your Majesty.

00:41:27.640 --> 00:41:31.440 line:80%
I've come to commend General Fan.

00:41:33.360 --> 00:41:36.960 line:80%
A few days ago, Your Majesty
mentioned those rumors

00:41:37.040 --> 00:41:38.200 line:80%
about the former Eastern Palace.

00:41:38.800 --> 00:41:40.640 line:80%
I've investigated thoroughly.

00:41:41.160 --> 00:41:43.560 line:80%
General Fan not only
killed Prince Changxin

00:41:43.640 --> 00:41:46.040 line:80%
on the battlefield
and rendered great service,

00:41:46.720 --> 00:41:51.720 line:80%
she also saved the bloodline
of Crown Prince Chengde,

00:41:52.560 --> 00:41:53.880 line:80%
the imperial grandson.

00:41:56.600 --> 00:41:59.760 line:80%
He is the direct heir
of the former Eastern Palace.

00:42:00.440 --> 00:42:03.200 line:80%
General Fan has performed
a great deed this time.

00:42:03.720 --> 00:42:05.800 line:80%
She deserves recognition for her valor.

00:42:09.120 --> 00:42:12.800 line:80%
What wonderful news!

00:42:12.880 --> 00:42:14.280 line:80%
Chancellor Wei,

00:42:15.040 --> 00:42:18.200 line:80%
the royal bloodline concerns
the very foundation of Dayin.

00:42:18.280 --> 00:42:19.400 line:80%
It cannot be mistaken.

00:42:20.000 --> 00:42:21.920 line:80%
Seventeen years ago,
the Eastern Palace fire

00:42:22.000 --> 00:42:24.840 line:80%
killed the crown prince's wife
and their son.

00:42:24.920 --> 00:42:26.160 line:80%
So,

00:42:26.720 --> 00:42:29.960 line:80%
how could this imperial great-grandson
appear out of nowhere?

00:42:30.040 --> 00:42:33.400 line:80%
And where is this person now?

00:42:33.480 --> 00:42:35.480 line:80%
After the Battle of Lucheng,

00:42:35.560 --> 00:42:38.320 line:80%
the imperial grandson indeed disappeared.

00:42:38.920 --> 00:42:41.800 line:80%
I request permission
to issue a reward decree.

00:42:41.880 --> 00:42:43.600 line:80%
Search the entire realm for him.

00:42:44.440 --> 00:42:47.360 line:80%
If we truly recover the royal bloodline,

00:42:48.040 --> 00:42:51.200 line:80%
it will ease Your Majesty's concerns
about succession.

00:42:53.320 --> 00:42:55.840 line:80%
As for true or false,

00:42:55.920 --> 00:42:58.520 line:80%
there are ways to determine that.

00:42:58.600 --> 00:43:01.680 line:80%
Even if the chance is slim,
we cannot give up.

00:43:01.760 --> 00:43:07.640 line:80%
Only thus can we honor
the late emperor's boundless grace.

00:43:11.480 --> 00:43:13.440 line:80%
The Chancellor speaks wisely.

00:43:13.520 --> 00:43:16.960 line:80%
I leave the matter of the reward
in your capable hands.

00:43:18.640 --> 00:43:23.080 line:80%
Be sure… Be sure to find my poor nephew.

00:43:29.400 --> 00:43:32.000 line:80%
Grandfather, please calm down.
Don't hurt yourself.

00:43:33.320 --> 00:43:36.200 line:80%
That Marquis of Wu'an…
Does he truly have fortune on his side?

00:43:36.960 --> 00:43:38.920 line:80%
Committing the gravest offenses,

00:43:39.000 --> 00:43:40.600 line:80%
yet evading consequence every time.

00:43:43.600 --> 00:43:44.440 line:80%
No.

00:43:44.960 --> 00:43:46.240 line:80%
Whatever it takes,

00:43:46.320 --> 00:43:49.960 line:80%
we must drive a wedge between uncle and
nephew, make them tear each other apart.

00:43:58.200 --> 00:43:59.440 line:80%
Send someone immediately.

00:43:59.960 --> 00:44:02.960 line:80%
Find a way to get word
to Xie Zheng by any means.

00:44:03.040 --> 00:44:05.160 line:80%
Tell him, 17 years ago,

00:44:05.240 --> 00:44:07.280 line:80%
on Wei Yan's way back to the capital,

00:44:07.360 --> 00:44:08.800 line:80%
he received a message from Lady Qi.

00:44:09.400 --> 00:44:12.240 line:80%
That's what led to the deaths
of his father, Xie Linshan,

00:44:12.320 --> 00:44:14.480 line:80%
and Crown Prince Chengde
of the Eastern Palace.

00:44:15.720 --> 00:44:17.800 line:80%
But that letter disappeared long ago.

00:44:18.320 --> 00:44:20.440 line:80%
Wei Yan has probably destroyed it by now.

00:44:20.520 --> 00:44:22.720 line:80%
A rumor is all it takes.

00:44:22.800 --> 00:44:25.680 line:80%
Xie Zheng will go looking for proof.

00:44:25.760 --> 00:44:31.640 line:80%
We just need them at each other's throats.

00:44:37.960 --> 00:44:39.520 line:80%
Seventeen years ago,

00:44:40.200 --> 00:44:43.320 line:80%
Wei Yan was too soft-hearted.

00:44:43.840 --> 00:44:48.280 line:80%
That's what led to today's disaster.

00:44:50.160 --> 00:44:53.200 line:80%
Now, we'll just…

00:44:54.240 --> 00:44:56.240 line:80%
set the stage again.

00:45:02.000 --> 00:45:04.920 line:80%
END CREDIT SCENE

00:45:05.800 --> 00:45:08.640 line:80%
GATHERING OF GRACE AND COMPASSION

00:45:08.720 --> 00:45:10.960 line:80%
Your Majesty, I've arrived.

00:45:14.880 --> 00:45:16.160 line:80%
I know it.

00:45:16.240 --> 00:45:21.360 line:80%
Not a single minister in this court
sees me as a true Son of Heaven.

00:45:21.440 --> 00:45:24.760 line:80%
Wei Yan treats me like a puppet emperor.

00:45:24.840 --> 00:45:26.880 line:80%
And Xie Zheng,
does he want to follow suit?

00:45:27.440 --> 00:45:29.320 line:80%
Find some descendant
of the former Eastern Palace,

00:45:29.400 --> 00:45:30.800 line:80%
then play them like a puppet?

00:45:31.480 --> 00:45:34.600 line:80%
Li Xiang, you worthless fool.

00:45:34.680 --> 00:45:36.040 line:80%
You even missed news

00:45:36.120 --> 00:45:39.360 line:80%
that a bloodline of the former
Eastern Palace is still alive.

00:45:39.440 --> 00:45:40.640 line:80%
And you,

00:45:40.720 --> 00:45:44.360 line:80%
do you want a new emperor to serve too?

00:45:44.440 --> 00:45:46.280 line:80%
Do you?

00:45:46.360 --> 00:45:47.280 line:80%
No, I don't.

00:45:47.360 --> 00:45:50.240 line:80%
I beg Your Majesty to calm down.

00:45:50.320 --> 00:45:55.240 line:80%
Please don't harm your dragon health
over this servant's failure.

00:45:55.760 --> 00:45:56.680 line:80%
Your Majesty,

00:45:57.200 --> 00:46:01.240 line:80%
this time, I truly did my best.

00:46:02.200 --> 00:46:06.240 line:80%
The Grand Princess wouldn't help me.

00:46:06.320 --> 00:46:08.400 line:80%
I was at my wit's end.

00:46:08.480 --> 00:46:13.120 line:80%
I had no choice but to risk death
and charge into the military camp.

00:46:13.200 --> 00:46:18.280 line:80%
And then,
the Marquis cut off one of my ears.

00:46:19.920 --> 00:46:24.800 line:80%
Your Majesty, I know I'm useless.

00:46:25.760 --> 00:46:26.640 line:80%
But…

00:46:27.600 --> 00:46:29.680 line:80%
But in my heart,

00:46:30.520 --> 00:46:32.120 line:80%
truly, in my heart,

00:46:32.200 --> 00:46:36.720 line:80%
there is only Your Majesty. Only you.

00:46:37.960 --> 00:46:39.600 line:80%
Come closer.

00:46:44.800 --> 00:46:46.920 line:80%
I'm here.

00:46:48.400 --> 00:46:49.840 line:80%
Does it hurt?

00:46:53.560 --> 00:46:56.120 line:80%
I… I'm fine.

00:46:56.200 --> 00:46:59.400 line:80%
It's healed now.

00:47:00.320 --> 00:47:04.120 line:80%
No. Whether it's Wei Yan or Xie Zheng,

00:47:04.200 --> 00:47:07.000 line:80%
no one sits on this dragon throne.

00:47:07.080 --> 00:47:09.720 line:80%
It's mine. No one.

00:47:09.800 --> 00:47:11.520 line:80%
Yes, Your Majesty.

00:47:11.600 --> 00:47:13.760 line:80%
You are the true Son of Heaven.

00:47:13.840 --> 00:47:16.240 line:80%
Those people aren't worthy.

00:47:16.320 --> 00:47:20.000 line:80%
No. You… You promise me.

00:47:20.080 --> 00:47:21.840 line:80%
You'll serve me forever. I am the emperor.

00:47:26.640 --> 00:47:27.680 line:80%
I…

00:47:29.720 --> 00:47:31.320 line:80%
obey the decree.

00:50:08.880 --> 00:50:11.960 line:80%
NO ANIMALS WERE HARMED
IN THE MAKING OF THIS EPISODE

00:50:12.040 --> 00:50:12.960 line:80%
Subtitle translation by: Wanjiao Song